name: Nothingness
body:
# Hacking Google Play
Google play is evolving and getting harder to figure out how it's working internally, for example, for latest version of auth:
`POST /auth HTTP/1.1
device: 32506279acbeb86e
app: com.google.android.gms
Accept-Encoding: gzip
User-Agent: GoogleAuth/1.4 (m2 LMY47D); gzip
content-length: 8682
content-type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Host: android.clients.google.com
Connection: Keep-Alive`
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
